        "timestamp": "2018-07-13 07:11:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nOleg, the introduction of this class is quite beneficial in the long run, when more APIs come into picture. This new file will serve as a common file to manage the API calls. For example, while doing a save all now in the reference page, we are calling the getArtifact API 4 times, one after the other. So, in a way we are writing the same piece of code4 times, which results in redundancy and in the future, it doesnt help in scalability as well. \nOnce, this file is merged, i will make changes to the application and call all the APIs through this file itself. I already have the code ready and regression tested.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
